events.description:
Help fill our library with love, all month long!  In honor of National Library's Month, drop by our&nbsp;children's area this month to pick up a special Valentine themed template.&nbsp;Children can color their masterpiece and write what they love most about the library! They can then deposit their creation&nbsp;in our special Valentine Letter Box.&nbsp;   Free!  All coloring supplies and templates provided.&nbsp; 
  Ages:  Perfect for toddlers through elementary schoolers. 
   ADA Accommodation
